  - "They too accept only responsibility, not identity of views"
- Wife **Rose D. Friedman**: "Pieced together the scraps of the various lectures, coalesced different versions, translated lectures into something more closely approaching written English"
  - "Has throughout been the driving force in getting the book finished"
